data.description: Beautiful Cape Cod near the beach, military bases, shopping, and quick access to the interstate. The neighborhood playground is within view of the property. First floor Primary Bedroom with an en suite, large eat-in kitchen with electric range that can be switched to gas, spacious laundry room, large back deck and detached garage with power, fully fenced in backyard. This home offers something for everyone nestled back in a quiet dog strollers dream. No HOA, not in a flood zone, clear termite and moisture in hand, 5 Bedrooms for this price is unheard of.
